619
00:33:32,430 --> 00:33:33,880
Anything on my face?

620
00:33:35,190 --> 00:33:35,800
Nope.

621
00:33:36,800 --> 00:33:37,710
Then why are you staring?

622
00:33:38,590 --> 00:33:39,560
You don't remember

623
00:33:39,560 --> 00:33:40,430
