637
00:34:22,230 --> 00:34:23,000
I'm not a fan

638
00:34:23,909 --> 00:34:24,999
Of the street food.

639
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:26,150
But roasted yam

640
00:34:26,870 --> 00:34:27,870
is an exception.

641
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,150
It was tasty.

642
00:34:34,230 --> 00:34:35,470
